node.text:
There is nothing like a pool which is set high on a cliff, with a view out over the sea, and one of the prettiest is the pool of @monasterosantarosa 
be sure to view this in reels for the full effect and be sure to tag someone who would love this 💙
Wishing everyone a great Saturday ! 
 
Video by @monasterosantarosa •

node.text:
Coming in hot! 
One of my all-time favorite videos by @marcovalmarana  of Drifter Cube (Owner: Andrea Bianchedi Captain: Andrea Viazzoli. Thank you @choc_croc )  making the turn into Portofino during the 2021 Regate di Primavera. 
Hats off to the captain for a masterful turn! 
To give us an idea of scale, this boat is 101 feet long and 122 feet high- that’s roughly the height of a 12 - 15 story building.
Be sure to watch this in Reels for the full effect and be sure to tag someone who might love it. 
And take a look at that beautiful little lighthouse – isn’t that a perfect spot!
We can watch this over and over again all weekend, as an antidote to the news. 
Sending love and good thoughts and wishing everyone a great weekend!
